Description: ====================
        Glamkit-commenttools
        ====================
        
        A tool for building user commenting apps. It is part of the `GLAMkit project <http://glamkit.org/>`_. For more information, see the `documentation <http://docs.glamkit.org/commenttools/>`_.
        
        View a full list of `GLAMkit components <http://docs.glamkit.org/components/>`_.
        
        
        Dependencies:
        =============
        
        - glamkit-stopspam (only if use_akismet == True)
